## Simulation test

We check that the precision formulae are correct by computing the observed covariance through simulations. 

<<test_cov.m -write>>=
addpath(genpath('Code'))
Xmt = 90:0.05:110;
par.C = 2; par.FWHM=3; par.Br = 101; par.v = 0.01; par.MA = 1;
